<div id="explanation">
<p><p><strong>Design your own T-Shirt with Spreadshirt</strong></p>
<p>Become a trend setter when you create your own t-shirt using Spreadshirt’s T-Shirt Designer.  Build your own t-shirt empire with stylish custom apparel from Spreadshirt.</p>

<p><strong>Make your own T-Shirt and Custom T-Shirt History</strong></p>
<p>The custom printed t-shirt became popular as a fashionable, stand-alone garment in the 1960s, when t-shirt designer Warren Dayton created his own political protest and pop-culture t-shirts.  When you create your own t-shirt with Spreadshirt’s T-Shirt Maker, you step into a long line of custom t-shirt designers.</p>

<p><strong>Print your own T-Shirt and Go Viral</strong></p>
<p>When you create your own t-shirt, you allow others to jump on the bandwagon and support you.  So design your own t-shirt and begin your rise to the top.  Spreadshirt makes it easy to create your own t-shirt and go viral by placing your custom designs on our Marketplace for all to see.</p></p>
